description: Collects Kiss: Psycho Circus #19-20.
Collects Kiss: Psycho Circus #21-22.

The man, the marvel, the human achievement, is back! From the cult movie starring Peter Weller, John Lithgow, Ellen Barkin, and Jeff Goldblum! The creators/filmmakers are telling new stories! Your favorite neurosurgeon/rock star/adventurer returns, along with his Hong Kong Cavaliers for an adventure where a Death's Head tank squad lurks in suburbia, talking bouncer-robots attack, expensive love wants to erupt, and Lectroids run with scissors, and then shotguns! The world may never be the same.

Brand new comic strip: 'A Short Sharp Lesson'

Bludgeon finds himself on the receiving end of Megatron's temper in an all-new comic strip n the latest all-action issue of TRANSFORMERS Comic!

Cruising for a Bruising

Demolisher loves nothing better then to 'Roll out' and cause carnage, while Optimus loves nothing better than stopping him! We take a look at these two giants of Cybertron at two key points during the history of TRANSFORMERS.

description: The world's heroines are whisked away to the Planet Rann to team up with Hawkgirl and Alana Strange against the mighty and evil Sinestra. Sinestra's focused her attention towards Earth, and these powerful women, armed with a weapon of incalculable power, are the planet's last hope!

Devastator blows stuff up. Due to the foldspace detonation, Devastator has been transported to an uninhabited alien world covered with cities.

Prelude: Ironhide

Hes one tough son-of-an-Allspark grizzled veteran, Ironhide, gets the movie prelude treatment in the latest issue of Transformers Comic! But thats just one small part of yet another rammed metal-storm mash-up of strips, features and competitons bring it on!

Transformers: Movie Prequel Part Five

Megatrons relentless pursuit of the Allspark brings him crashing down on Planet Earth in a place called Antarctica. Things are going to get messy for the weakened Decepticon leader in the latest part of the fantastic comic-strip prequel to the Transformers movie!

Beast Wars: The Gathering Part Five

An ancient race of Transfomers crash on prehistoric Earth and, imitating the animals they find, the brutal Beast Wars commence! The race is on as the evil Predacons try and stop the Autobot infiltrator, Razorbeast, from warning Cybertron about Magmatrons masterstroke!

description:
Prelude: Jazz

If youve seen the Transformers movie, youll know that Jazz met a grisly end at the hands of Megatron, but thats not to say he doesnt soldier on in the pages of the latest issue of Transformers Comic! Find out how he got to Earth in the first place in our prelude story.

Movie Special

Check out this issues special feature celebrating the Transformers movie stars Shia La Boeuf and Megan Fox talk about the film, its making, and their careers! The movies finally out on DVD this Christmas, and were giving away loads of copies in this issues competition!

Beast Wars: The Gathering Part Six

Preshistoric Earth, 70,000 years ago. An ancient race of Transformers crash on the planet, and the Beast Wars commence! In part six, the net closes on the heroic Maximals, who find themselves trapped and facing slaughter at the hands, claws and teeth of the evil Predacons!

Starscreams Militia

Starscream takes centre stage in a brand-new story in the latest issue of Transformers Comic! With the smoke barely cleared from downtown LA and the dust barely settled after Megatrons demise, Starscream seizes his chance to take command of the Decepticons!

Transformers: Movie Prequel Part Seven

Megatron on ice is a conundrum for his human discoverers to contemplate in the latest part of the fantastic comic-strip prequel to the Transformers movie. Will the Hoover Dam become home sweet home for the Decepticon leader? Also in this issue, the ferocious Beast Wars continue!

How to draw Megatron

Grab your pencil and paper and learn to draw the mechanoid master of malevolence with our fantastic guide! Plus, win great Transformers prizes in our awesome competitions, and check out an excusive pull-out poster by the legendary Transformers artist Geoff Senior!

Twilight's Last Gleaming: Part Two

The second skull-shattering segment of Twilights Last Gleaming kicks off the new issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC! History continues to be rent asunder as Megatron rules the earth and humanity itself is on the ropes. Can things get any worse for the desperate Autobots?

Beast Wars: The Gathering Part Ten

All kinds of hell are kicking off on Earth 70,000 years ago as the brutal 'Beast Wars' continue, everyones favourite Dinobot, Grimlock, opens a new front! Also in this issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC, the comic strip prequel to the TRANSFORMERS movie continues!

Transformers Animated

TRANSFORMERS COMIC gives you the lowdown on quite possibly the greatest animated television series in the history of mechanoid lifeforms! The TRANSFORMERS juggernaut continues to thunder on with TRANSFORMERS ANIMATED, blazing away on screens right now!

Twilights Last Gleaming: Part Three

Disaster looms for the Autobots in the new issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC, as the action in Twilights Last Gleaming spreads to the moon. Things are looking cosmically bad for the Autobots, as their plans to save Earth from Decepticon tyranny prove hopelessly optimistic.

Beast Wars: The Gathering Part Eleven

The brutal action of Beast Wars continues in the new issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC, as Fate and Ravage finally catches up with the Maximal infiltrators. Plus, in the latest chapter of the TRANSFORMERS movie prequel, dark forces gather on Earth as the Decepticons arrive in their masses.

Transformers Animated: Prime Candidates

Meet the Autobot stars of the new all-action cartoon series TRANSFORMERS ANIMATED, airing weekdays on Nickelodeon at 4:30pm. Plus, cranking things up yet another notch, we pitch two heavy-hitters at one another in this issues How To Draw its Barricade v Ironhide!

description:
Twilights Last Gleaming: Part Four

Mikaelas infiltration of Decepticon HQ has revealed that Optimus Prime is Megatrons prisoner and giving the term on ice a whole new meaning! The few remaining Autobots are locked in one last final struggle to free their beloved leader in the new issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC!

How to Draw Blackout

We like to take the art tutorials up a notch in each issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC. This time around, try your hand at Blackout as he transforms! Also in this issue, the unrelenting mayhem and chaos of Beast Wars and the movie prequel story continues.

Win Transformers merchandise!

The much-loved board game Risk has been updated and re-invented now the Autobots and Decepticons wage war for control of Cybertron and the AllSpark! Dont miss your chance to win this awesome game, and loads more, in the new issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC!

Twilights Last Gleaming: Part Five

Not one, not two, but three yes, three stories reach their epic conclusions in the new issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC! In the final part of Twilights Last Gleaming, Optimus Prime has come in from the cold and hes all hot and bothered. Megatron beware!

Beast Wars: The Gathering Part Thirteen

Its Maximals v Predacons as the war on Ice Age Earth reaches its final showdown in Beast Wars. Plus, the TRANSFORMERS movie prequel comic strip reaches its thrilling conclusion as Decepticons and Autobots close in on the current resting place of the AllSpark!

TRANSFORMERS ANIMATED BONUS PULL-OUT!

Theres awesome news about TRANSFORMERS ANIMATED in the new issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC, and youll find it in a 16-page special pull-out section! Check out a whole shed-load of comic strips, features, posters and profiles on the latest members of the TRANSFORMERS Universe.

Aftermath Part 1

The battle may be won but the war is not over for Optimus Prime and the Autobots theyre going to need a pretty big broom to clean up the mess left behind. Worse still, Humanity is none to pleased with its supposed protectors, and you wouldnt like Humanity when its angry!

Competitions

Dont miss your chance to win awesome prizes! Action-packed anime video game Appleseed: Ex Machina, Thundercats DVD box sets, and classic and contemporary TRANSFORMERS action figures are all up for grabs in this issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC!

Beast Wars: The Ascending Part 1

The Beast Wars enters a brutal new chapter in this issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC. Magmatrons efforts to reactivate a dormant army of Predacons have failed and now he is missing presumed dead. Meanwhile, Razorbeasts Maximals and Ravages Predacons have been stranded in time

Aftermath Part 2

Humanity breaks out the big guns on all robot lifeforms in this issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC! As Earth enters its death throes and organic life is eaten alive by the AllSpark's metal power, the Autobots prepare a plan that stands as much chance of destroying the planet as saving it!

How to Draw: Frenzy

The Decepticons key infiltrator has a funny, squeaky voice, and hes psychotic. Follow an in-depth tutorial in drawing the chittering chaos that is Frenzy in this issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC, and send in your motorised masterpieces to the usual address!

Beast Wars: The Ascending Part 2

Retrax and Manterror are preparing an ambush for any unwary Maximal but suddenly find that the hunter is now the hunted. The remorselessly brutal conflict of the 'Beast Wars' continues as the fallout from Magamatrons defeat and disappearance kicks in.

A brand new story of epic proportions begins in the latest giant-size issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC. With everything going to hell on Earth, the Autobots must make a desperate return to their home planet in the hope of averting the destruction of their adopted world.

A bumper comic needs bumper prizes, and weve got some awesome gear up for grabs in this issue. Win a portable DVD player, Next Avengers games, giant Hulk smash hands, a Nintendo DS console, and radio-controlled helicopters!

Transformers Animated The latest news and Preview Comic Strip!

If you dont know by now, TRANSFORMERS ANIMATED COMIC launches on 23 October, and this issue features an exclusive preview strip by TRANSFORMERS legend Simon Furman. Visit our TRANSFORMERS ANIMATED page and get all the intel in the first issue!

description:
Return to Cybertron Part 6: Hard Target

With Unicron destroyed, Optimus Prime and the Autobots face another threat in the latest issue of TRANSFORMERS Comic. Starscream has seized control of Earth and turned the remaining humans against their one-time saviours, and the Autobots return home has turned somewhat bumpy

Gen. 1: Megatron Origin Part 8

Kaon security forces, led by the powerful Sentinel Prime, are hunting down the Transformers who ply their trade in underground fight clubs in the hope of winning fame and fuel. And who should be the rising star of this brutal, and often legal spectacle? You guessed it...Megatron!

Beast Wars: The Ascending Part 8

The arrival of Rartorata interrupts Ravages plans to leave the rock we call Planet Earth in the latest chapter of Beast Wars. Meanwhile, as the energy source Angolmois wreaks havoc on Cybertron, has the Transformers home planet entered a new age the age of Shokaract?

description:
The Decepticon Who Haunted Himself

Starscream is having a few mental problems in the latest issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC his Decepticon army has taken control of the Earth once more, outnumbering and outgunning the Autobots, but can Megatrons successor take the pressure of the hot seat?

Competitions

The latest issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC offers you the chance to win the ultimate old-school gaming package were giving away an X-Box 360 and a copy of the Sega Mega Drive Ultimate Collection! Plus, check out the comics Top Gear section and win brilliant new books and TRANSFORMERS toys from Hasbro!

Beast Wars: The Ascending Part Nine

The addictive energy source Angolmois is threatening to bring Cybertron to its knees in the latest chapter of Beast Wars: The Ascending. Can Ravage bring the Maximals and Predacons together to face the real threat? Plus, check out our profile of Longrack the most terrifying giraffe ever!

Revolution: Part One

Prepare for incredible nuclear-tipped shocks in the latest issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC, as Starscreams plans begin to come to fruition in Revolution. The US President has been duped into ordering the Autobots off Planet Earth, but thats nothing compared to whats coming next!

Competitions

Were giving away loads of cool gear in the latest issues competitions. Dont miss out on your chance to win a Nintendo Wii and Sonic and the Black Knight games, a DVD player and Tales of Despereaux DVDs, and an awesome TRANSFORMERS bedroom set, including duvet and curtains.

Transformers Animated: Divebomb

TRANSFORMERS Animated returns to the hallowed pages of TRANSFORMERS COMIC in the latest issue, as chaos sets in on Dinobot Island. With the US Airforce about to test their new stealth bomber and a Decepticon rogue in their midst, the Autobots need some aerial support and fast!

Revolution: Part Two

With the Autobots destroyed in the incredible shock ending in the previous issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC, Earth is there for the taking in the latest chapter of Revolution. Still, not all the Decepticons are happy with Starscreams unique style of insane leadership

Top Gear: Competitions

Were giving away a Nintendo DS console and five copies of the new puzzle game The Humans: Meet The Ancestors in the latest issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC. Plus, there are TRANSFORMERS toys and other goodies up for grabs!

Transformers Animated: Megatrons Revenge

Buckle up for more action from 22nd Century Detroit in the latest issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC. When Afterburn is exposed as a Decepticon spy, the Autobots are left fighting for their circuits as their HQ comes under a surprise attack from the villainous Megatron and his henchbots

Revolution: Part Three

Starscreams plans seem to have finally borne fruit, and its all getting really ugly on Planet Earth in the latest issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC. As the Decepticon leader goes into mental meltdown, the battle to save the Autobots adopted home enters its final endgame! Is it all over?

Beast Wars The Ascending: Part Twelve

Sworn enemies unite in the latest chapter of the brutal 'Beast Wars', as the heroic Maximals and evil Predacons come together to prevent Cybertron and Ice Age earth falling to the awesome might of the entity known as Shokaract. Its time for a glorious last stand!

Transformers Animated: The Race

The latest issue of TRANSFORMERS COMIC features a brand new TRANSFORMERS Animated story, starring 20th Century Detroits finest heroes. Bumblebee breaks his own record for delivering Saris cheese pizza but is he the fastest thing on four wheels? Theres only one way to find out!
